my-claw/sdp/prd-embodiment-interaction-loops.md:21:| EMBLOOP-004 | Implement responsive Theramini output generation from the live interaction loop, with bounded latency and clear routing through the audio/MIDI stack. | MUST | T2 | - MIDI output reaches Theramini from a playable path<br/>- Latency is measured and reported<br/>- Failures degrade gracefully without crashing the organism |
