my-claw/sdp/prd-glyphweave-art-studio.md:14:2. **Two-phase LLM generation** — free reasoning/planning phase, then constrained grid output
my-claw/sdp/prd-glyphweave-art-studio.md:43:│  │ - plan phase │  │ - model grid │  │ - browse/filter       │ │
